title: Greens Up! - Main Street
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Salad bar restaurant offering quick salads made with fresh local ingredients, including some organic, and in-house dressings. The Thai salad is vegan, and you can build your own salad. Large portions. Also offers a muddling bar with farmers market fruit and herbs to be mashed into organic ice tea and California lemonade. Bags and cups are made from plants and are biodegradable. Prices cheap to moderate. Has Wi-Fi. Nov 2013 note no longer offering soup.
